reasons 1.4 (A) and (D). 
 
(C) We delivered reftel points April 7 to Javier Carbajosa, 
Senior Advisor to the Foreign Ministry\'s Ramon Gil-Casares, 
Secretary of State for Foreign Affairs (GOS\'s deputy 
 
