TAGS: PREL, PGOV, AF, SP 
SUBJECT: SPAIN UNDETERRED BY FAHIM\'S REMOVAL FROM VICE 
PRESIDENTIAL TICKET 
 
REF: STATE 162903 
 
Classified By: KATHLEEN M. FITZPATRICK, POLITICAL COUNSELOR. 
REASONS 1.4 (B) & (D) 
 
(C)  We met with Carlos Morales, Deputy Director General for 
Continental Asia (and former Deputy DG for Pacific, Southeast 
Asia and the Philippines Affairs) August 2 to hear whether 
Spain\'s engagement in Afghanistan would be affected by 
President Karzai\'s decision to remove Fahim Khan from the 
