RACISM, XENOPHOBIA, AND DISCRIMINATION 
 
REF: STATE 176189 
 
1.  (U)  The Spanish MFA has told us that Foreign Minister 
Miguel Angel Moratinos will be leading the Spanish delegation 
to the Organization for Security and Cooperation in Europe 
