STATE PASS EB/ESC/TFS (BSTEPHENSON), S/CT (TKUSHNER), 
NEA/ARP (TWILLIAMS), NEA/ELA (DBARON), IO/PHO (APEREZ), NSC 
(MRUPPERT), TREASURY (JZARATE), OFAC (RNEWCOMB) 
 
E.O. 12958: DECL: 09/29/2015 
TAGS: CVIS, EFIN, ETTC, PREL, PTER, KTFN, SP, LVPR 
SUBJECT: TERRORIST FINANCE: JAMA\'AT AL TAWHID WA\'AL-JIHAD 
(JTJ) DESIGNATION 
 
REF: STATE: 208513 
 
Classified By: Econ: Carl Schonander based upon reasons 1.4(b) and (d) 
 
 (S) EconOffs delivered reftel demarche to Spain\'s Financial 
Intelligence Unit (SEPBLAC) on 9/29/04.  SEPBLAC officers 
said they would use the information in reftel demarche in 
checking their databases for relevant information.  EconOffs 
also delivered on 9/29/04 the demarche to the MFA\'s Miguel 
Enrique Garcia Herraiz.  He said his \"initial\" reaction was 
that it should not be a problem for Spain to support adding 
the JTJ to the UN\'s 1267 Sanctions Committee\'s consolidated 
list of individuals/entities.  Herraiz said he would send the 
information we provided him to Spain\'s UN mission.  EconOffs 
will also be delivering reftel demarche to the Ministry of 
Economy. 
MANZANARES 
"
