"21673","10/15/2004 15:42","04MADRID4020","Embassy Madrid","UNCLASSIFIED//FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY","04MADRID3273|04MONTEVIDEO1390","This record is a partial extract of the original cable. The full text of the original cable is not available.

