Glyn Davies, Deputy Assistant Secretary of State to travel to 
Madrid and Barcelona, October 19-22. 
 
2.  Control Officer at Embassy Madrid is Political Officer 
Robert J. Riley.  He can be reached at work (34-91-587-2392), 
on his mobile (34-609-057-454) or e-mail:  rileyrj@state.gov. 
Control Officer at Consulate Barcelona is Consul General Juan 
Alsace.  He can be reached at work (34-93-280-2227 ext. 203), 
on his mobile (34-649-295-948) or e-mail:  alsaceJA@state.gov. 
 
